parameters:
I designed this suspension bridge ahead. You can jump with the
confirm button.

If you're using touch controls, face the direction you want to go
and click on your current location. Hmm... this doesn't really
give me a sense of exhilaration.

But, it's fun, you know?... I hope it brings a smile to your
face, even just a little.
\i[385] I obtained the Magical Care Alpha! \$

We made this suspension bridge together as twins. I hope it can
distract me a little bit...
It looks like the residence of twin lumberjacks.

I was watching my sister's trampoline jump... It's not bad. I
think she has a sense for it.
